
<div class="tidal_current_wrap">
	<div class="tidal_img">
		<!--<img src="../../images/page/img_tidal_current_page.jpg" alt="">-->
		<div id="tidal_map" style="width:100%;height:250px;">
	</div>
	<div class="table table_center table_border table_tidal">
		<table>
			<caption></caption>
			<colgroup>
				<col style="width:21%;">
				<col style="width:19%;">
				<col style="width:18%;">
				<col style="width:15%;">
				<col style="width:32%;">
			</colgroup>
			<thead>
			<tr>
				<th scope="col">대상</th>
				<th scope="col">지점</th>
				<th scope="col">단계</th>
				<th scope="col">발령일</th>
				<th scope="col">기관</th>
			</tr>
			</thead>
			<tbody>
			{{#each tidal.getJsonData}}
			<tr>
				<td>{{alertObject}}</td>
				<td><a href="#" class="btn_map" style="text-decoration: underline">{{alertPoint}}</a></td>
				<!--<td><span class="round_signal icon_signal_{{stageCode}}"></span>{{stage}}</td>-->
				<td>{{{stageChange stageCode}}}</td>
				<!--<td>{{stage}}</td>-->
				<td>{{substring alertDate 5}}</td>
				<td>{{alertInstitute}}</td>
			</tr>
			{{/each}}
			</tbody>
		</table>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="tidal_alarm">
	<div class="table table_center table_border table_blue">
		<table>
			<caption></caption>
			<colgroup>
				<col style="width:25%;">
				<col style="width:75%;">
			</colgroup>
			<thead>
			<tr>
				<th scope="col">경보단계</th>
				<th scope="col">발령 해제 기준(상수원 구간)</th>
			</tr>
			</thead>
			<tbody>
			<tr>
				<td><span class="signal_left_wrap"><span class="round_signal "><img src="/images/egovframework/mkwip/map/pin01.png" width="10" /></span>미발령</span>	</td>
				<td class="align_left">채취 시 남조류 세포수가 1,000세포 / ㎖ 미만일 경우</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><span class="signal_left_wrap"><span class="round_signal "><img src="/images/egovframework/mkwip/map/pin02.png" width="10" /></span>관심</span></td>
				<td class="align_left">2회 연속 채취 시 남조류 세포가 1,000세포/㎖이상 10,000세포/㎖미만인 경우</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><span class="signal_left_wrap"><span class="round_signal "><img src="/images/egovframework/mkwip/map/pin03.png" width="10" /></span>경계</span></td>
				<td class="align_left">2회 연속 채취 시 남조류 세포가 10,000세포/㎖이상 1,000,000세포/㎖미만인 경우</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><span class="signal_left_wrap"><span class="round_signal "><img src="/images/egovframework/mkwip/map/pin04.png" width="10" /></span>대발생</span></td>
				<td class="align_left">2회 연속 채취 시 남조류 세포가 1,000,000세포/㎖ 이상인 경우</td>
			</tr>
			</tbody>
		</table>
	</div>
</div>
	